&lt;li&gt;Responsible for managing relationships with specific NGOs (“Strategy relationship manager”) by staying up to date on the evolution of their strategy/ies, coordinating with the Philanthropy team on donor stewardship, serving as the GCS communication point to the NGO, and documenting communications in our knowledge management system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
