&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively plan Leadership Team meetings, ensuring prep, timing, optimized agendas, and preparation for smooth flow and excellent follow-up in partnership with the President.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Staff the Leadership Team in ongoing conversations between strategic planning processes, as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan regular leadership team retreats, including developing objectives, agendas, and pre-read materials, to review progress against Climate Lead’s current strategic plan or other key objectives for the LT (e.g., team formation or board formation) and iterate as needed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft memos and agendas that crisply tee up key discussions and decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
